	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You anoint an enchanted creature's forehead with powdered diamond dust, repeating a cleansing phrase or mantra that draws out magical afflictions.</em></p><p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require 0.2 pounds of pure @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wV3r0XKYOLYdI0nz]{Diamond Dust}, typically valued at 100 gold. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><strong>Healing Spell</strong></p><p>You remove one of the following from the target:</p><ul><li>All of the following: &amp;reference[charmed], &amp;reference[confused], &amp;reference[frightened], &amp;reference[goaded], &amp;reference[petrified], &amp;reference[silenced], and &amp;reference[siphoned] conditions.</li><li>All curses, including the target's attunement to a &amp;reference[cursed] magic item.</li><li>A creature possessing the target, which appears in a space of their choice within 5 ft. of the target.</li></ul><p></p><p><em>This spell cannot remove a condition caused by a disease or another condition not listed (eg. a version of poisoned that causes creatures to also be confused).</em></p>",
